data.description: Welcome to this north facing 5-bedroom, 3.5 bath First Texas Home, located in a highly sought-after Prosper ISD school district. With its impressive features and thoughtful design, this residence offers the perfect blend of functionality. Step inside to discover an open-concept floor plan that effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The well-appointed kitchen boasts sleek countertops, abundant cabinetry, and SS appliances, and butlers pantry. The large dining area is ideal for hosting gatherings. The main floor features a primary suite, complete with a private ensuite bathroom and roomy walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll find four additional bedrooms, each offering comfort and privacy and a large game room, which his perfect for leisure or activities. The presence of wood floor tile throughout adds a touch of elegance and ensures easy maintenance. The spacious 3-car garage provides ample storage space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable home your own.
